Package org.robotalons.lib.motion.actuators

Class Module

java.lang.Object
org.robotalons.lib.motion.actuators.Module
All Implemented Interfaces:
Closeable, AutoCloseable
Direct Known Subclasses:
FlywheelModule, SparkModule
public abstract class Module extends Object implements Closeable

Singular unit which assists in the control of motion throughout the competition field, which provides implementation for control of both an azimuth (Rotation) motor, which controls the angle or direction of the module, and a linear (translation) motor which controls the velocity or magnitude of the module.

      public abstract void periodic()
      This method is called periodically by the CommandScheduler. Useful for updating subsystem-specific state that you don't want to offload to a Command. Teams should try to be consistent within their own codebases about which responsibilities will be handled by Commands, and which will be handled here.
